<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="idca390b3b-3a70-11f1-bde1-a5140e158598" identifier="/us/usc/t43/s1471i"><num value="1471i">§ 1471i.</num><heading> Availability of appropriations for services or rentals</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">Annual appropriations made to the Department of the Interior shall on and after <date date="2004-12-08">December 8, 2004</date>, be available for obligation in connection with contracts issued for services or rentals for periods not in excess of 12 months beginning at any time during the fiscal year.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="idca390b3c-3a70-11f1-bde1-a5140e158598">(<ref href="/us/pl/108/447/dE/tI/s106">Pub. L. 108–447, div. E, title I, § 106</ref>, <date date="2004-12-08">Dec. 8, 2004</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/118/3063">118 Stat. 3063</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
